<%= render "marketing_nav" %>

<section class="relative overflow-hidden landing-hero-drench pt-24 pb-20" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-hero-pattern"></div>
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-1"></div>
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-2"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-16">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#b8d4b5] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">For Finance Officers</p>
        <h1 class="landing-hero-title text-balance text-5xl leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          Your financial position.<br>
          <span class="landing-hero-accent">Always current.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="landing-hero-body mt-6 max-w-xl text-balance text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Every transaction flows directly into your books — no re-entry, no spreadsheet reconciliation,
          no waiting for branch reports. Trial balance, income statement, balance sheet — all ready
          when you need them, not at the end of the month.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="#demo" class="landing-hero-cta landing-hero-cta-primary">See It in Action</a>
          <a href="/session/new" class="landing-hero-cta landing-hero-cta-outline">Try a Demo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <div class="landing-browser-frame">
          <div class="landing-browser-toolbar">
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#ff5f57"></span>
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#ffbd2e"></span>
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#28c840"></span>
          </div>
          <img src="<%= image_path('screenshots/dashboard.svg') %>" alt="Financial dashboard in Sirib">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-[#f0f7ef] border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-12" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">200+</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">journal entries recorded per day</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">2 hrs</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">month-end close time</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">0</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">manual reconciliation errors</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-3" style="top: -5rem; right: 15%; opacity: 0.6;"></div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#5b8c5a] uppercase mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">The Flow</p>
      <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#1c1917] sm:text-4xl">
        How transactions flow into your financial statements
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-4" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 1</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Transaction recorded</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Teller posts a transaction. Sirib immediately generates the corresponding journal entry — debit, credit, account — automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2"/><path d="M9 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v0a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 2</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Journal entry posted</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Double-entry posted to the general ledger in real time. Finance officer reviews or approves — no data re-entry from branch reports.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5.586a1 1 0 0 1 .707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 0 1 .293.707V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 3</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Trial balance</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Running trial balance always available. Balances are live, not at month-end. Officers can run it any time — it reflects everything posted that day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 3h18v4H3zM3 10h12v4H3zM3 17h6v4H3z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 4</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Financial statements</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Income statement, balance sheet, cash flow statement — generated from live data. One click to produce. No spreadsheet assembly required.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-[#faf9f7]" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#5b8c5a] uppercase mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">What Gets Automated</p>
      <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#1c1917] sm:text-4xl">
        The tasks Sirib handles so finance officers work on analysis
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 4h16v4H4zM4 10h12v4H4zM4 16h6v4H4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Recurring journal entries</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Depreciation, accruals, and subscriptions — scheduled to post automatically. Finance officer reviews instead of re-entering the same entries every period.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M8 7h12M8 12h12M8 17h12M4 7h.01M4 12h.01M4 17h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Inter-account transfers</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Moving funds between accounts logged and posted as a journal entry pair. Full audit trail — who initiated, who approved, what the purpose was.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 7a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v4a2 2 0 0 1-4 0V7z"/><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0 9 9 0 0 0-18 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Provision calculations</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">IFRS 9 expected credit loss provisions computed from loan portfolio data. System calculates based on aging buckets and past-due records — officer reviews and approves.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="M18 9l-5 5-4-4-3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Cash flow projections</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">30/60/90-day cash flow projected from recorded transactions and scheduled payments. Available anytime — not just when the treasurer compiles the report.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-white" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#5b8c5a] uppercase mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">Manual Tasks Offloaded</p>
      <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#1c1917] sm:text-4xl">
        What your finance officers won't have to do anymore
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#faf9f7] rounded-lg p-5 border border-[#e7e5e4]">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#5b8c5a]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6e6358]">Re-entering transaction data from branch reports into the accounting system</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#faf9f7] rounded-lg p-5 border border-[#e7e5e4]">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#5b8c5a]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6e6358]">Reconciling bank statements manually — every transaction ties to a journal entry</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#faf9f7] rounded-lg p-5 border border-[#e7e5e4]">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#5b8c5a]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6e6358]">Assembling financial statements from spreadsheets — generated from live data in one click</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#faf9f7] rounded-lg p-5 border border-[#e7e5e4]">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#5b8c5a]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6e6358]">Posting paper ledger entries by hand — every transaction flows from source to ledger</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#faf9f7] rounded-lg p-5 border border-[#e7e5e4]">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#5b8c5a]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6e6358]">Calculating depreciation and accruals manually — scheduled entries post automatically</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-[#faf9f7] rounded-lg p-5 border border-[#e7e5e4]">
        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-[#5b8c5a]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#6e6358]">Waiting for branch reports to close the books — everything is real time</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-[#f0f7ef] relative overflow-hidden" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-4" style="bottom: -8rem; left: 10%; opacity: 0.5;"></div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-[#b8d4b5] mb-8">
        <span class="landing-metric">3 days → 2 hours</span>
      </div>
      <blockquote class="text-2xl font-normal tracking-[-0.02em] text-[#1c1917] leading-relaxed">
        "Month-end used to be three days of pulling numbers from branches, reconciling, and correcting. The last few months we've been closing in two hours. Not because we work faster — because Sirib already has everything posted."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Finance Manager</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#6e6358]">Mindanao Cooperative Bank</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="demo" class="landing-cta-band border-b border-[#e7e5e4] relative overflow-hidden" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-1" style="opacity: 0.15;"></div>
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-2" style="opacity: 0.15;"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24 text-center">
